Improve
=======

Syntax:
  improve <skill>

Spend one pending skill slot to raise a skill you already know. Each slot
adds that skill's normal per-level percentage (varies by skill, usually +4
or +5). You earn one pending slot each time you advance a level with the
advance command.

Examples:
  improve first aid
  improve wp knife
  improve prowl

Check pending slots on score. List your skills with the skills command.

See also: skills, advance, score
